{"tid":1227680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該聽日遊行要拎白玫瑰","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:52:21.000Z","uid":19794,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"001e31c748fc77cd4833313341d4e41bb3f61c3e","tid":1227680,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"白玫瑰（德語：Die Wei&szlig;e Rose）是納粹德國時期一個知名的非暴力反抗組織，其成員包含了慕尼黑大學中的許多學生及教授，主要是由漢斯&middot;蕭爾）、蘇菲&middot;蕭爾、克里斯多福&middot;波普斯特（Christoph Probst）、亞歷山大&middot;許墨瑞、庫特&middot;胡伯和維利&middot;格拉夫（Willi Graf）所領導。而此團體之所以為人所知乃是因為其於1942年6月至1943年2月間陸續發送了6張未具名的傳單，主要內容在於呼籲人們參加反抗希特拉政權的運動。<br />\n<br />\n白玫瑰的6名核心成員於1943年時被蓋世太保逮捕，並於同年被送上斷頭台。而他們所散發的第6份傳單後來由法學家赫爾穆特&middot;詹姆斯&middot;馮&middot;毛奇帶出德國，並輾轉透過北歐流入英國，且於1943年7月被大量印刷後透過同盟國的飛機發散在德國境內，其標題為：「慕尼黑學生的聲明」（The Manifesto of the Students of Munich）[1]。<br />\n<br />\n由於他們無懼於死亡而仍堅持對抗第三帝國的統治，白玫瑰的成員們在今日廣受德國人尊敬，且幾乎被視為是英雄。如同馮&middot;毛奇所言，「它們搭起了通往無納粹世界的橋梁」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRip"},{"pid":"a9e1c06a30b9631ab3f218305d9f1f890f0b04cf","tid":1227680,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761998ecea976c0cc8cae864318ee9f349593f09","tid":1227680,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaef3a2b92bc42131bb0da8d15b6752a31fc447","tid":1227680,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime